rComments: I love this prof with my whole heart. A lecture was never boring. He marked fair and his class was easy to follow along with. This course is entertaining and thought provoking as it is. Would recommend 10/10 , also a real cutie ;p
Best teacher ever! Super interesting, mind opening! Good grades easy t get! Everyone should have a course with him!!!

took psychology of evil, excellent professor. Especially very good at connecting various fields to make a coherent explanation of different phenomena we classify under 'evil'. Also encourages critical thinking and allows for the raising of objections and questions in class. Assignments are easy but worth doing.
